5.  Show Receive PON Power in OLT

show pon power attenuation gpon-onu_1/2/2:17
           OLT                  ONU              Attenuation
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
 up      Rx :-4.000(dbm)       Tx:2.509(dbm)        6.509(dB)      
 
 down    Tx :6.449(dbm)        Rx:-1.838(dbm)       8.287(dB)

